{"word":"G4848 - συμπορεύομαι - symporeúomai - soom-por-yoo'-om-ahee - Go with","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συμπορεύομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">symporeúomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soom-por-yoo'-om-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Go with</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கூடவா, கூடப்போ"},{"paragraph":"1. to go or journey together"},{"paragraph":"2. to come together, to assemble"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G4198 - πορεύομαι - poreúomai - por-yoo'-om-ahee/4198\">G4198</a>; to <i>journey together</i>; by implication to <i>assemble:</i> - go with, resort.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}